323
00:15:59,160 --> 00:16:00,460
... bevi lo shottino...

324
00:16:02,600 --> 00:16:05,400
... e poi mordi il lime.

325
00:16:10,100 --> 00:16:13,830
Mi spiace, non ho sentito
niente dopo "leccare".

326
00:16:14,600 --> 00:16:18,060
Collo, shottino, lime.

327
00:16:26,430 --> 00:16:27,760
Okay, shottino, lime.

328
00:16:27,830 --> 00:16:29,360
Giusto.

329
00:16:36,060 --> 00:16:37,130
